original_title: Pup School: Up in the Clouds
overview: Pup School is back in session and cuddly pups Moxie and Bo are ready to learn from their super smart teacher, Professor Twiggles. This time the pup team take to the sky to learn all about the fluffy stuff that makes up clouds!
tagline: Flying into a new learning adventure!
title: Pup School: Up in the Clouds
